Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在胡说八道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来还有运动系文化节了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是！
